==Personal life==
Newberger is married to Michele Newberger. They have three daughters and reside in [[Becker, Minnesota]].<ref name="about">{{cite web | url=http://www.jimforminnesota.com/about.html | title=About the Candidate | publisher=Jim Newberger for HD15B | work=Jim Newberger for Minnesota House District 15B | accessdate=April 3, 2013}}</ref>

